  ('social-worker-moex-01401', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '機構工作人員在將需求調查問卷資料輸入電腦時，因為精神不濟，有時將4打成3，有時將2打 成3，此種錯誤稱為：', '["系統誤差", "隨機誤差", "理論誤差", "抽樣誤差"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3e07f321dfb8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cf21ad8c6d04", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01402', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-109-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種抽樣方法所抽取出來的樣本最具有母體代表性？', '["理論抽樣（theorticalsampling）", "滾雪球抽樣（snowballsampling）", "深度抽樣（intensitysampling）", "分層抽樣（stratifiedsampling）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3e07f321dfb8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cf21ad8c6d04", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
